791static inline bool setJSHTMLMediaElement_srcSetter(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSHTMLMediaElement& thisObject, JSValue value)
792{
793 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject);
794 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
795 CustomElementReactionDisallowedScope customElementReactionDisallowedScope;
796 auto& impl = thisObject.wrapped();
797 auto nativeValue = convert<IDLUSVString>(lexicalGlobalObject, value);
798 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
799 invokeFunctorPropagatingExceptionIfNecessary(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope, [&] {
800 return impl.setAttributeWithoutSynchronization(WebCore::HTMLNames::srcAttr, WTFMove(nativeValue));
801 });
802 return true;
803}

1936JSC::IsoSubspace* JSHTMLMediaElement::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1937{
1938 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1939 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1940 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLMediaElement.get())
1941 return space;
1942 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLMediaElement> || !JSHTMLMediaElement::needsDestruction);
1943 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLMediaElement>)
1944 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLMediaElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLMediaElement);
1945 else
1946 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLMediaElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLMediaElement);
1947 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLMediaElement.get();
1948IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1949IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1950 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSHTMLMediaElement::visitOutputConstraints;
1951 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1952 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1953 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1954IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1955IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1956 return space;
1957}

1959void JSHTMLMediaElement::analyzeHeap(JSCell* cell, HeapAnalyzer& analyzer)
1960{
1961 auto* thisObject = jsCast<JSHTMLMediaElement*>(cell);
1962 analyzer.setWrappedObjectForCell(cell, &thisObject->wrapped());
1963 if (thisObject->scriptExecutionContext())
1964 analyzer.setLabelForCell(cell, "url " + thisObject->scriptExecutionContext()->url().string());
1965 Base::analyzeHeap(cell, analyzer);
1966}

1968bool JSHTMLMediaElementOwner::isReachableFromOpaqueRoots(JSC::Handle<JSC::Unknown> handle, void*, AbstractSlotVisitor& visitor, const char** reason)
1969{
1970 auto* jsHTMLMediaElement = jsCast<JSHTMLMediaElement*>(handle.slot()->asCell());
1971 auto& wrapped = jsHTMLMediaElement->wrapped();
1972 if (!wrapped.isContextStopped() && wrapped.hasPendingActivity()) {
1973 if (UNLIKELY(reason))
1974 *reason = "ActiveDOMObject with pending activity";
1975 return true;
1976 }
1977 if (jsHTMLMediaElement->wrapped().isFiringEventListeners()) {
1978 if (UNLIKELY(reason))
1979 *reason = "EventTarget firing event listeners";
1980 return true;
1981 }
1982 if (JSNodeOwner::isReachableFromOpaqueRoots(handle, 0, visitor, reason))
1983 return true;
1984 UNUSED_PARAM(visitor);
1985 UNUSED_PARAM(reason);
1986 return false;
1987}

1991 auto* jsHTMLMediaElement = static_cast<JSHTMLMediaElement*>(handle.slot()->asCell());
1992 auto& world = *static_cast<DOMWrapperWorld*>(context);
1993 uncacheWrapper(world, &jsHTMLMediaElement->wrapped(), jsHTMLMediaElement);
1994}
